snippet.title: Nixon Talks
snippet.description:
Thank you for subscribing.

An Aussie man from Sydney. Putting my thoughts and opinions into the public sphere as well as reactions.
Current topics, sports, politics, social themes and even the odd societal titbit.

Also co-host of the 2 Men Podcast - https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCfCSv842pe2j32Ri_PAgzfA

Audio podcast available too (sometimes audio only versions of videos) - Search 'Nixon Talks'  on Spotify or podcast platforms.

Drop a DM or message to Instagram or Twitter.
